  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA64">
<l>icainta varavamum veṟpuṅ kaṭalum</l>
<l>pacaintaṅ kamutu paṭuppa – vacaintu</l>
<l>kaṭainta varuttamō kacciveḵ kāviṟ</l>
<l>kiṭantiruntu niṉṟatuvu maṅku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lying, sitting and standing there in Kacci, in Veḵkā,</l>
<l>is that endurance for [him who] churned to exhaustion</l>
<l>in order to bring forth the ambrosia there after having united</l>
<l>the consenting snake, mountain and ocean?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
